title: Grateful Dead Live at Boston Garden on 1994-10-02
lineage: Dat > Panasonic SV-3700 > Tascam DA-3000 > wav 16/48; Edited & Mastered in Audacity by Joe Noel: wav 16/48 > flac 16/48; Checksum & tags created in xACT
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, Loser, It's All Over Now, Row Jimmy, Broken Arrow, Mama Tried*-> Mexicali Blues*, Tennessee Jed, Picasso Moon

Set 2

Iko Iko, Samba In The Rain, If The Shoe Fits, Samson & Delilah, Crazy Fingers-> Truckin'>, That Would Be Something-> Jam-> Drums-> Space-> The Days Between-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: U.S. Blues

* Weir on acoustic guitar
